data.description: ***Investors Only*** Tenant occupy until 11/30/2024. Great property with an amazing backyard! Large covered patio, with an impeccable outdoor kitchen and refrigerator.  No carpet in the house!  Upgrades all throughout! Beautiful wood-like tile on the first floor. Modern arrow floors in the kitchen.  Gorgeous updated kitchen featuring quartz countertops, white cabinets, breakfast nook and close by laundry room. Very tasteful fireplace accent wall. All bedrooms upstairs. Marble floors upstairs. Very large recently painted Master bedroom with in-suite updated 5 pieces bathroom.  Good size secondary bedrooms. Great game room upstairs.
